---
title: Caramelized Honey-Garlic Turkey Noodles with Snow Peas and Sesame Seeds
description: Surprised to see linguine in an Asian-inspired dish? Well, don't be! Linguine is a heartier noodle that holds onto sauce without weighing it down, making it an ideal vehicle for tonight's sweet chili sauce!
